HEADWORD: Forestage
<hw>For"est*age</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>forestage</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(O. Eng. Law)</fld> <sd>(a)</sd>
<def>A duty or tribute payable to the king's foresters.</def>
<sd>(b)</sd> <def>A service paid by foresters to the king.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

